fix: product cards stuck invisible after clearing search filter

Removed viewport={{ once: true }} from the grid container's whileInView
config. This caused newly mounted child motion.div elements to inherit
initial="hidden" (opacity: 0, y: 32) without ever receiving the "show"
variant — because whileInView had already fired its single permitted time
on the previous render cycle.

